{"tid":1936097,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"眾說 封不了人心","createTime":"2020-03-21T04:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T04:35:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"631a3b6abecfe1f5323c56e9943e9351a0767fc3","tid":1936097,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"眾說<br />\n封不了人心<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 心義 | 發佈日期: 20.03.20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3-%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-20200320162738_b691_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-20200320162738_b691_small.jpg&h=75e09943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片由筆者提供<br />\n<br />\n還有兩個星期就考DSE作文，心情很緊張喔！出街影吓相睇吓有什麼幫助作文的靈感。<br />\n<br />\n各區連儂牆，相信被暴政封得的&mdash;&mdash;封了；清洗的&mdash;&mdash;就徹底清洗，全被封殺！<br />\n<br />\n行到九龍灣連儂牆，早前被宣傳東九文化中心的大幅膠布所遮蓋，但港人仍繼續於膠布上張貼各種抗爭及抗疫文宣，結果也被清光。<br />\n<br />\n其後政府用綠色假草封了部份鋼板，但「你有食屎計，港人也有翻牆梯」！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者使用噴漆噴上文宣，雖然很快也被暴政清洗，但港人從沒有放棄宣洩對暴政不滿機會。<br />\n<br />\n早兩天路過，見有工程人員，再用綠色膠草將餘下鋼板施行全面封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3-%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-20200320162711_20ae_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-20200320162711_20ae_small.jpg&h=075c8b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3-%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-20200320162728_f848_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-20200320162728_f848_small.jpg&h=1155fe2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28071/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-28071/%E5%B0%81%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28071%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-28071%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583&h=28acfbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這代表了，只會不斷打壓，不服從者，趕盡殺絕，看看不斷到各區拘捕年青人，便知港共軟不手軟，容不下反對聲音，只懂得用口罩收買人心，這是管治之道？<br />\n<br />\n我們也無需來個硬碰，正好就這時機，想一想，如何備戰9月立法會選舉，奪取更多議席，誓要踢走保皇黨，特別功能組別裡令人厭惡的「吔蚊張」，以及只懂得於會議廳內瞓覺的「黃訂光」。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭仍未完結，有些事情，香港人永遠不會忘記。<br />\n<br />\n封殺了各區連儂牆又如何，封不了人心！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=0b04a646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n博客 | 心義<br />\n【心義・中學女生抗爭日常】去年夏天之前，我是一個只識考試，打籃球，追韓星金宇彬的傻女生，但去年6月9日後，我好似變咗......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28071/%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%81%A3-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-28071/%E5%B0%81%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28071%2F%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%2584%2582%25E7%2589%2586-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-28071%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583&d=KoefzaQl